headline: DoorDash, Williams-Sonoma, Expand, & TKO Group join S&P 500
summary: DoorDash (DASH), Williams-Sonoma (WSM), Expand Energy (EXE), and TKO Group Holdings (TKO) joined the S&P 500 (^GSPC). Morning Brief hosts Brad Smith and Madison Mills discuss how the stocks are reacting. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief here.
